tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE women_owned_businesses (
  business_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  business_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  owner_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  business_type VARCHAR(50),
  location VARCHAR(100),
  description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE women_owned_businesses (
    business_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    business_name VARCHAR(255),
    owner_name VARCHAR(255),
    location VARCHAR(255),
    industry VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    business1_id INT,
    business2_id INT,
    collaboration_note VARCHAR(255),
    FOREIGN KEY (business1_id) REFERENCES women_owned_businesses(business_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (business2_id) REFERENCES women_owned_businesses(business_id)
);

CREATE TABLE women_businesses (
    business_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    business_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    owner_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    city TEXT NOT NULL,
    state TEXT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE business_contacts (
    contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    business_id INT,
    contact_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    email TEXT NOT NULL,
    phone_number TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE women_businesses ( 
    business_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    business_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    owner_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    business_category VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, 
    location VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL 
);

CREATE TABLE business_contacts ( 
    contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    business_id INT NOT NULL, 
    contact_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    contact_email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15) NOT NULL, 
    FOREIGN KEY (business_id) REFERENCES women_businesses(business_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE business_reviews ( 
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    business_id INT NOT NULL, 
    reviewer_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    review_rating INT NOT NULL, 
    review_comment TEXT, 
    FOREIGN KEY (business_id) REFERENCES women_businesses(business_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE business_events ( 
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    business_id INT NOT NULL, 
    event_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    event_date DATE NOT NULL, 
    event_location VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    FOREIGN KEY (business_id) REFERENCES women_businesses(business_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE women_owned_businesses (
    business_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    business_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    owner_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    business_type VARCHAR,
    location VARCHAR,
    founding_year INTEGER
);

CREATE TABLE business_contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    business_id UUID,
    contact_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR,
    contact_phone VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE business_reviews (
    review_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    business_id UUID,
    reviewer_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    review_rating INTEGER,
    review_comment TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE business_events (
    event_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    event_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    event_date DATE,
    event_location VARCHAR,
    organizer_name VARCHAR,
    business_id UUID
);
